♪Autumn leaves drift and fall♪

566
00:42:12,690 --> 00:42:14,580
♪Snow piles thick before the house♪

567
00:42:14,580 --> 00:42:18,100
♪The seasons change and blend as one♪

568
00:42:18,100 --> 00:42:21,070
♪The figure in the mirror
lowers their eyes♪

569
00:42:21,070 --> 00:42:27,030
♪Love and hatred, gratitude
and grievance, spoken only in silence♪

570
00:42:28,520 --> 00:42:31,170
♪A gilded promise written in a book♪

571
00:42:31,170 --> 00:42:33,070
♪Legends of love and hate♪

572
00:42:33,070 --> 00:42:36,610
♪Left for time to decide♪

573
00:42:36,610 --> 00:42:40,900
♪If you are one who knows me,
and you are still waiting for me♪

574
00:42:40,900 --> 00:42:44,550
♪Regret, do not forget♪

575
00:42:44,550 --> 00:42:47,020
♪Combing through the threads
of coming and going♪

576
00:42:47,020 --> 00:42:49,120
♪A whirlpool of right and wrong♪

577
00:42:49,120 --> 00:42:52,440
♪Left to the years to carve at will♪

578
00:42:52,660 --> 00:42:56,740
♪When this door is opened♪

579
00:42:57,140 --> 00:43:00,400
♪Within a palm's breadth,
a thousand years♪
